channel.title: New 531 Cache models
channel.description:
Hello everyone,
I recently decided to start looking through my model files to find models to add to my server.
Here are some i wanted to show off to you peeps.
I will release one section of models of everyone's choice depending on replies.
If i get too many votes and views and next to no posts, I will release NOTHING.
Also, all models will be converted to 317 and a copy of 531 will be kept with it when i give the release link. (If i do.)
BTW, DO NOT say i leeched from rune-server, ad my name on rune server is rock me plox, the one who posted them on rune-server...... -.-
[size=16pt][b][u][i]Dragon Plate & Plate Pieces + Galkon of Rune-Server's D claw piece concept:[/i][/u][/b][/size]
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/14uawi0.png[/img]
[B][I][SIZE=16pt][U]Miasmic Spells:[/U][/SIZE][/I][/B]
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/rhvpmf.png[/img]
[U][I][B][SIZE=16pt] Tele-block Spell[/SIZE][/B][/I][/U]
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/348jerb.png[/img]
[B][I][U][SIZE=16pt] Dagon'hai and Elite:[/SIZE][/U][/I][/B]
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2h6xeex.png[/img]
[SIZE=10pt]I Also have ALL of the wield models for the wearable stuff... so DW.
Sorry about not posting some of the models listed.. was too lazy to do it, busy programming anyway.
On sunday i will take the poll results and release the most voted on models and release them posting a link here, and on rune-server.
Any questions, comments, concerns? pm me on this forum, rune servers forum, or my msn @ garrettgs@hotmail.com :D
[B][COLOR=Orange][SIZE=12pt]Post away![/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]
